<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.9.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2021-07-14T20:41:43+00:00</updated><id>/feed.xml</id><title type="html">MignoloLab</title><subtitle>...nulla si crea, nulla si distrugge, tutto si trasforma.</subtitle><entry><title type="html">Realizzare del pastone per uccelli</title><link href="/projects/pastone_uccelli/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Realizzare del pastone per uccelli" /><published>2021-05-16T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2021-05-16T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/pastone_uccelli</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/pastone_uccelli/">&lt;p&gt;
Il pastone per uccelli selvatici o domestici, si pu&amp;ograve; fare direttamente a casa con ingredienti facilmente reperibili
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Procuratevi una ciotola capiente ed un mestolo.&lt;br&gt;
Ingredienti necessari:&lt;br&gt;
125g farina 00&lt;br&gt;
250g farina di mais (per polenta)&lt;br&gt;
300g semi misti pr uccelli&lt;br&gt;
250g margarina
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Inserite la faria 00 nel recipiente
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Poi la farina di mais.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Infine in	serite i semi.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Mescolate bene il tutto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Tagliate a cubetti la margarina.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Fatela sciogliere bene sul fuoco.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Quando sar&amp;agrave; sciolta, inseritela con gli altri ingredienti.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Mescolate bene il tutto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/10.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Lasciate raffreddare un pochino.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/11.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Fate delle palline piccole.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/12.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Chiudete la pallina in una retina.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/13.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Il pastone &amp;egrave; pronto..
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://youtu.be/imAE5K9SCt8&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-low" /><summary type="html">Il pastone per uccelli selvatici o domestici, si pu&amp;ograve; fare direttamente a casa con ingredienti facilmente reperibili</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Trasformare della stoffa avanzata in una mascherina</title><link href="/projects/mascherina_fai_da_te/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Trasformare della stoffa avanzata in una mascherina" /><published>2020-03-23T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2020-03-23T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/mascherina_fai_da_te</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/mascherina_fai_da_te/">&lt;p&gt;
Pu&amp;ograve; essere utile avere una mascherina per il viso da usare in diverse situazoni, &amp;egrave; possibile crearla con degli carti di un maglione.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/mascherina_fai_da_te.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Procuratevi il layout della mascherina e stampatelo.&lt;br&gt;
Io ho usato questo PDF:
&lt;a href=http://tianascloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Face-mask.pdf&gt;Download&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
Successivamente ritagliate la forma.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Ricavatene due parti uguali.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cucite i bordi,per evitare che la tela si sfilacci.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Posizionate le due parti &quot;paccia a faccia&quot;, in modo da nascondere la cucitura.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cucite la parte frontale e rigirate la maschera.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cucite l'elastico dalle due parti laterali della mascherina.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ripiegate la stoffa per aumentare la resistenza.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;La mascherina &amp;egrave; terminata.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/mascherina_fai_da_te.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://youtu.be/7AuVwNzcFK4&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-medium" /><summary type="html">Pu&amp;ograve; essere utile avere una mascherina per il viso da usare in diverse situazoni, &amp;egrave; possibile crearla con degli carti di un maglione.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Riutilizzare un vecchio maglione</title><link href="/projects/maglione_presine/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Riutilizzare un vecchio maglione" /><published>2019-10-18T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-10-18T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/maglione_presine</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/maglione_presine/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Come si pu&amp;ograve; recuperare un maglione?&lt;br&gt;
Una delle possibilit&amp;agrave; &amp;egrave; la seguente.
&lt;/p&gt;
Procuratevi un vecchio maglione e scucitelo come in foto.
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Disegnate la forma di una presina, vi faciliterà il taglio della stoffa.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Tagliate due parti per presina come si vede in foto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;
Cucite la stoffa a specchio ma non completamente, lasciate un lato libero, vi servir&amp;agrave; per rigirare la presina.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
Aggiungete all'interno un pezzetto di stoffa per creare l'asola, come in foto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Finite di cucire, lasciando un piccolo spazio per rigirare la presina. 
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/10.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/11.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Finite di cuire la presina con ago e filo
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/12.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Fate lo stesso per le altre presine aggiungendo, dove necessario, un piccolo bordo.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/13.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/14.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B2EmaYwj2dA&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-medium" /><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Recuperare una pianola abbandonata</title><link href="/projects/restauro_pianola/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Recuperare una pianola abbandonata" /><published>2019-09-07T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-09-07T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/restauro_pianola</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/restauro_pianola/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Come si pu&amp;ograve; recuperare una pianola elettronica abbandonata?
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

La prima cosa da fare &amp;egrave; smontare tutta la pianola.&lt;br&gt;
Dividendo i componenti in plastica, ferro ed elettronici.
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ora si puliscono le parti in plastica e metallo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Si sistema il circuito eletronico eventualmente abbia dei componenti arrugginiti.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
E si riparano i componenti in plastica rotti.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/10.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
Si rimontano le componenti elettroniche.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/11.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/12.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
Si mette del grasso sui pulsanti, per facilitarne il movimento.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/13.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/14.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Si rimontano i componenti in plastica.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/15.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
Si scartavetrano le compoenti metalliche.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/16.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
Per poi verniciarle.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/17.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
Finito il montaggio si passa al test finale.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;
&lt;img style=&quot;margin: 10px&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/18.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UX9o_M7TKqc&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-low" /><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Recupero di grate in legno</title><link href="/projects/recupero_grate/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Recupero di grate in legno" /><published>2018-08-30T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-08-30T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/recupero_grate</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/recupero_grate/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Con il tempo le grate in legno hanno bisogno di una ristrutturazione.&lt;br&gt;
La cosa non &amp;egrave; molto difficile, ora vi dimostro come fare.&lt;br&gt;
Procurtatevi le grate da ristrutturare.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Con della carta vetrata togliete tutta la vecchia vernice.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pulite la grata con dello straccio imbevuto di acqua.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Passate due mani di fondo (o turapori), vi servir&amp;agrave; per proteggere il legno dalle intemperie.&lt;br&gt;
Per i tempi di essiccazione affidatevi alle tempistiche del produttore.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Passate due mani di colore (il colore che preferite).
Per i tempi di essiccazione affidatevi alle tempistiche del produttore.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Infine rimontate il tutto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://youtu.be/BBe7swVUd4o&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-medium" /><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Trasformare bottiglie in serre</title><link href="/projects/bottiglia_serra/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Trasformare bottiglie in serre" /><published>2018-03-24T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-03-24T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/bottiglia_serra</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/bottiglia_serra/">&lt;p&gt;
Si possono creare dele piccole serre riutilizzando delle bottiglie di plastica.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Procuratevi una bottiglie di plastica, andranno bene qualsiasi bottiglie di plastica, l'importante che abbiano il corpo ondulato come quelle in foto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Tagliate la prima bottiglia poco dopo l'ondulazione, come in foto.&lt;br&gt;
Potete usare un taglierino
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Una volta tagliata la bottiglia praticate una piccola incisione.&lt;br&gt;
Questa servir&amp;agrave; a facilitarela chiusura.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Inserite dell'acqua nella parte bassa della bottiglias.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Inserite la pianta.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Chiudete la bottiglia.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Posizionate la bottiglia vicino ad una finestra.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lrkW-71-7Og&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-low" /><summary type="html">Si possono creare dele piccole serre riutilizzando delle bottiglie di plastica.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Recuperare delle batterie al litio</title><link href="/projects/recuperare_batterie/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Recuperare delle batterie al litio" /><published>2018-02-21T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-02-21T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/recuperare_batterie</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/recuperare_batterie/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;362&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Per i vari progetti di elettronica &amp;egrave; possibile recuperare delle batterie al litio modello 1865 o 18650, in modo facil e sicuro.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;362&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Iniziamo con l'aprire il pacco batterie del laptop con una taglierina e un cavviatite.&lt;br&gt;
Quando effettuate questa operazione state attenti a non forare le batterie al litio pedrch&amp;egrave; potrebbero esplodere.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;362&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Una volta aperto il pacco batterie, vedrete le batterie e duna scheda elettronica come in foto.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;362&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Rimuovete la scheda, in questo progetto non ci serve, e tagliate i cavi che la collegano alle batterie.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;363&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Ora togliete tutti i supporti di collegamento delle batterie aiutandovi con delle pinze.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;362&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Alla fine otterrete le batterie pronte per essere caricate ed utilizzate nei vostri progetti.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;363&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Vi consiglio di controllare ogni singola batteria con il tester per vedere se sono funzionanti o completamente scariche.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;363&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=481LA37UP5o&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-medium" /><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Piccola valigetta per il primo soccorso</title><link href="/projects/primo_soccorso/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Piccola valigetta per il primo soccorso" /><published>2017-04-08T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2017-04-08T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/primo_soccorso</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/primo_soccorso/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Procuratevi un contenitore per gelati
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Con della carta vetrata rimuovete la serigrafia.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Verniciate di bianco la confezione.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Disegnate una croce sul coperchio.&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Nastrata i margini con del nastro carta.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Verniciate di rosso e rimuovete il nastro carta.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/10.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Inserire l'occorrente.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/11.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Un ipotetico KIT pu&amp;ograve; contenere il seguente materiale:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Due garze sterili 18X40&lt;br&gt;
Due cerotti a nastro&lt;br&gt;
Alcool etilico o disinfettante&lt;br&gt;
Fazzoletti&lt;br&gt;
Forbici&lt;br&gt;
Clip ferma bende&lt;br&gt;
Due bende 4m per 6cm &lt;br&gt;
Guanti in lattice&lt;br&gt;
Cotone idrofilo&lt;br&gt;
Accendino&lt;br&gt;
Coperta termica
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
La cassetta &amp;egrave; terminata.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/12.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gYgLK1J831E&amp;spfreload=10&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-low" /><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Regalo personalizzato</title><link href="/projects/regalo_personalizzato/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Regalo personalizzato" /><published>2017-01-19T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2017-01-19T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/regalo_personalizzato</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/regalo_personalizzato/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/10.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
In questo tutorial vi spiego come personalizzare un regalo, in particolare dei bicchieri di vetro.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Prima di tutto, procuratevi i bicchieri che volete personalizzare e rimuoveteli dalla confezione, senza romperla.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.png&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Ora con il dremel, disegnate la decorazione che più vi piace, oppure il nome della persona che ricever&amp;agrave; il regalo.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Ritagliate un pezzo di carta da regalo, grande abbastanza da coprire la confezione dei bicchieri.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Applicate la colla come in foto.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Incollate la carta regalo alla scatola dei bicchieri.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Tagliate la carta in eccesso.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Riconfezionate i bicchieri con il nuovo rivestimento.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Il regalo &amp;egrave; terminato, ora pu&amp;ograve; essere spedito.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.png&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nNVe9nTtVj8&amp;spfreload=10&gt;Fare click qui per il video&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="difficulty-medium" /><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Trasformare un block notes in due quaderni</title><link href="/projects/quaderni/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Trasformare un block notes in due quaderni" /><published>2016-12-22T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2016-12-22T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/projects/quaderni</id><content type="html" xml:base="/projects/quaderni/">&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Un block notes A4, a volte &amp;egrave; pi&amp;ugrave; ingombrande di due quaderni A5, con questo tutorial potete risolvere il problema.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Iniziamo con il bloccare con delle mollete la parte inferiore del block notes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/2.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ora, con della Vinavil o colla simile, incolliamo l'estremit&amp;agrave; appena bloccata&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/3.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Per evitare che le pagine si spostino, aggiungiamo delle mollette in pi&amp;ugrave;, per fissare il tutto ed aspettiamo che la colla si asciughi.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/4.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Dividiamo per 5 la larghezza del block notes cos&amp;igrave; da ricavare 4 punti per la rilegatura.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/5.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Pratichiamo i fori con un chiodino o un trapano a punta fine.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/6.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Passiamo alla rilegatura con dello spaga, io ho usato del filo da pesca.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/7.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Dividiamo per due la lunghezza del block notes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/8.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
E tagliamo con un taglierino, in modo da ottenere due piccoli quaderni.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/9.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Ora si passa alla copertura, procuriamoci delle immagini che vi piacciono.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/10.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Posizioniamo i quaderni sopra per vedere se ricoprono tutta l'immagine e piegatene i bordi per creare delle dime che ci serviranno per incollaggio.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/11.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Incolliamo l'immagine e ritagliamo i bordi in eccesso.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/12.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/13.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Ritagliamo un pezzo di carta con spessore di 2,5 centimetri e lungo poco pi&amp;ugrave; del quaderno ed incolliamolo al lato dello stesso per ricoprire la rilegatura.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/14.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Tagliate le eccedenze.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 10px 0&quot;&gt;
&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;images/15.jpg&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Fate lo stesso anche con l'altro quaderno ed abbiamo finito.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
